This topic describes how to install, configure, and upgrade the TIBCO BusinessWorks Container Edition Buildpack for Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF).

##<a id='install'></a> Install and Configure the TIBCO BusinessWorks Container Edition Buildpack 

1. Download the product file from Pivotal Network.

1. Upload the product file on the Ops Manager Installation Dashboard.

1. Click **Add** next to the uploaded TIBCO BusinessWorks Container Edition Buildpack tile in the Ops Manager **Available Products** view to add it to your staging area.

1. Click the newly added **TIBCO BusinessWorks Container Edition Buildpack** tile.

1. Specify values for the configuration options. (**Which options?**)

1. Click the **Stemcell** tab. Download the correct stemcell from Pivotal Network and click **Import Stemcell** to import it.

1. Click **Save**.

1. Return to the Ops Manager Installation Dashboard and click **Apply Changes** to install the tile.

##<a id='upgrade'></a> Upgrade the TIBCO BusinessWorks Container Edition Buildpack

1. Download the latest version of the product from Pivotal Network.

1. Upload the new product file to Ops Manager.

1. Upload the stemcell associated with the update, if required.

1. Update any new mandatory configuration parameters, if required.

1. Click **Save**.

1. Click **Apply Changes** to install the upgraded tile.
